title: 25W: Will A&M Buy-Out Jimbo Fisher? + Eric Wood Talks Playing in Buffalo & Post-NFL Career + Bobby's Power Rankings
itunes:title: 25W: Will A&M Buy-Out Jimbo Fisher? + Eric Wood Talks Playing in Buffalo & Post-NFL Career + Bobby's Power Rankings
description:
With Texas A&M looking worse by the week - both on and off the field - Kickoff Kevin asks Bobby how much longer Jimbo Fisher can stick around before Texas A&M is forced to buy him out. Plus, former Bills center Eric Wood joins Bobby to discuss playing in Buffalo, the ins and outs of playing offensive line, and his business ventures since he retired a few years ago. After some trades around the league this week, Bobby discusses his power rankings heading into Week 8.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
